name: OAuth2KeycloakLib
description:
This project have the code for OAuth 2.0 access JWT Token validation with Spring Security. Keycloak Server is use as authorization server and in short is responsible of issuing an access token.
So every microservice need to validate access token, by using this lib as jar depencency, we just need to set SecurityConfig.java file for more refernce please see the movie application project.
